latestIgtvVideos.title: 20 years to Lateralus (TOOL)
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
🎧 if you can. 🌀

"I embrace my desire to
I embrace my desire to
Feel the rhythm, to feel connected
Enough to step aside and weep like a widow
To feel inspired
To fathom the power
To witness the beauty
To bathe in the fountain
To swing on the spiral
To swing on the spiral to
Swing on the spiral
Of our divinity
And still be a human"

To those of you who are under 20;
I wrote this.

Air pollution hacks from a clown, pt 2 

From @deadant.live ’s ‘Laughs Per Minute - Breathless Edition’ in Mumbai; where 25 comedians performed one-minute sets taking aim at air pollution.

Now that you’ve caught your breath, check out @climate_communicators , a credible source of information about air pollution!
